's  consort,  Prince Albert of Saxe-Coburg-Gotha ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Meurig Ap Meurig Lloyd was born in Nannau, Merionethshire, Wales, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Malli verch Hwyel."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1330–Female":"1330–Surnud","1330":"1330","about 1330":"umbes 1330","of Ceinmeirch, Nannau, Llanfachreth, Merionethshire, Wales":"Merionethshire, Wales","of Nannau":"Nannau, Merionethshire, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1330–Female":"1330–Kuollut","1330":"1330","about 1330":"noin 1330","of Ceinmeirch, Nannau, Llanfachreth, Merionethshire, Wales":"Merionethshire, Wales","of Nannau":"Nannau, Merionethshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1330–Female":"1330–Décédée","1330":"1330","about 1330":"environ 1330","of Ceinmeirch, Nannau, Llanfachreth, Merionethshire, Wales":"Merionethshire, Galles","of Nannau":"Nannau, Merionethshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Meurig Ap Meurig Lloyd est né à Nannau, Merionethshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Malli verch Hwyel."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1330–Female":"1330–Verstorben","1330":"1330","about 1330":"um 1330","of Ceinmeirch, Nannau, Llanfachreth, Merionethshire, Wales":"Merionethshire, Wales","of Nannau":"Nannau, Merionethshire, Wales, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Meurig Ap Meurig Lloyd wurde in Nannau, Merionethshire, Wales, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Malli verch Hwyel mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","–Female":"Desede","–Male":"Desede","1330–Female":"1330–Desede","1330":"1330","about 1330":"about 1330","of Ceinmeirch, Nannau, Llanfachreth, Merionethshire, Wales":"Merionethshire, Wales","of Nannau":"Nannau, Merionethshire, Pays de Galles, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","–Female":"elhunyt","–Male":"elhunyt","1330–Female":"1330–elhunyt","1330":"1